{"tid":1553134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Repost] 新屋嶺入面到底發生咗乜嘢事，我想大家去諗清楚","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T09:22:05.000Z","uid":229709,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e53d1fa857dc8fed9df98b239be0d0205462509b","tid":1553134,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺入面到底發生咗乜嘢事，我想大家去諗清楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547870</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［Repost]<br />\n屌！呢個post推極都推唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢位師兄講嘅野 真心好有道理！<br />\n新屋嶺無cctv，啲狗為所欲為。<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益<br />\n如果受害人喺狗屋/ 新屋嶺 比人強姦/ 輪姦，<br />\n除咗受害人親自企出黎指證之外，<br />\n仲會唔會有其他方法？<br />\n<br />\n班女仔仲好細個，<br />\n而家肯定成世有陰影。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要幫佢討回公道，<br />\n「一個都不能少」唔係單單係口號<br />\n我地係貫徹始終 言出必行去幫呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人認為：<br />\n除咗狗局內發生嘅女女女 比較難做到真正FC外<br />\n其他嘅news 一定要FC 先好傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好重蹈雨傘嘅覆轍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住呀受害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要你承受呢啲壓力 係香港人欠咗你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天佑我城。"},{"pid":"d5146f1b0f1c0fe1e39fc487540cb4b5dad55148","tid":1553134,"uid":229709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"推呀 集思廣益<br />\n如果短期內未有大量市民關注/ 追究<br />\n我怕狗局內嘅情況會愈黎愈不受控 同 變本加厲"},{"pid":"caae8a690f292cb64c6daa0aaba81b7cda4fa54b","tid":1553134,"uid":229